# UC-02: Auto Assign Lead

## Use Case ID

UC-02

## Use Case Name

Auto Assign Lead

## Description

This use case assigns newly created leads to the appropriate sales representative based on predefined business rules.

## Primary Actor

Salesforce System

## Secondary Actor

Sales Manager

## Preconditions

* Lead record exists.
* Assignment rules are configured.

## Trigger

New lead is created.

## Main Flow

1. System identifies lead location.
2. System identifies dealership branch.
3. System identifies available sales representative.
4. System assigns lead automatically.
5. Notification is sent to assigned representative.
6. Assignment activity is logged.

## Alternate Flow

3A. No representative is available.

* Lead is assigned to Sales Manager.

## Postconditions

* Lead is assigned.
* Notification is delivered.

## Business Rules

* Assignment based on dealership region.
* Round-robin assignment method used.

