# UC-03: Qualify Lead

## Use Case ID

UC-03

## Use Case Name

Qualify Lead

## Description

This use case evaluates customer interest and determines whether a lead should proceed to the sales pipeline.

## Primary Actor

Sales Representative

## Preconditions

* Lead is assigned.
* Customer contact information exists.

## Trigger

Sales representative contacts customer.

## Main Flow

1. Representative reviews lead information.
2. Representative contacts customer.
3. Customer requirements are discussed.
4. Vehicle preferences are captured.
5. Purchase timeline is identified.
6. Budget information is collected.
7. Lead qualification status is updated.

## Alternate Flow

7A. Customer not interested.

* Lead status updated to "Closed - Not Interested".

7B. Unable to contact customer.

* Follow-up task created.

## Postconditions

* Lead qualification status updated.

## Business Rules

* Qualified leads proceed to opportunity stage.
* Unqualified leads remain in nurture process.

