# UC-04: Schedule Test Drive

## Use Case ID

UC-04

## Use Case Name

Schedule Test Drive

## Description

This use case allows sales representatives to schedule vehicle test drives for qualified customers.

## Primary Actor

Sales Representative

## Secondary Actor

Customer

## Preconditions

* Lead is qualified.
* Vehicle is available.

## Trigger

Customer requests a test drive.

## Main Flow

1. Representative opens customer record.
2. Representative selects vehicle.
3. Available time slots are displayed.
4. Representative confirms preferred slot.
5. Test drive appointment is created.
6. Confirmation email is sent.
7. Appointment appears on dealership calendar.

## Alternate Flow

3A. Vehicle unavailable.

* Representative selects alternative vehicle.

## Postconditions

* Test drive appointment scheduled.
* Customer receives confirmation.

## Business Rules

* Appointment must have vehicle and location assigned.
* Confirmation notification mandatory.

