# UC-05: Create Opportunity

## Use Case ID

UC-05

## Use Case Name

Create Opportunity

## Description

This use case converts a qualified lead into a sales opportunity.

## Primary Actor

Sales Representative

## Preconditions

* Lead status is Qualified.
* Customer expresses purchase intent.

## Trigger

Customer decides to proceed with purchase discussion.

## Main Flow

1. Representative opens lead record.
2. Representative selects "Convert Lead".
3. System creates Account.
4. System creates Contact.
5. System creates Opportunity.
6. Opportunity assigned to representative.
7. Opportunity enters sales pipeline.

## Alternate Flow

5A. Duplicate customer exists.

* Existing account linked.

## Postconditions

* Opportunity created successfully.

## Business Rules

* Only qualified leads can be converted.
* Opportunity owner must match lead owner.

