# UC-06: Manage Follow-Up Activities

## Use Case ID

UC-06

## Use Case Name

Manage Follow-Up Activities

## Description

This use case ensures timely engagement with customers throughout the sales cycle.

## Primary Actor

Sales Representative

## Secondary Actor

Salesforce System

## Preconditions

* Lead or Opportunity exists.

## Trigger

Follow-up action is required.

## Main Flow

1. System generates follow-up task.
2. Representative receives reminder.
3. Representative contacts customer.
4. Interaction details recorded.
5. Follow-up status updated.
6. Next action scheduled.

## Alternate Flow

3A. Customer unavailable.

* New follow-up task scheduled.

## Postconditions

* Communication history maintained.

## Business Rules

* Every qualified lead must have an active follow-up task.
* Follow-up reminders generated automatically.

