# UC-07: Generate Performance Reports

## Use Case ID

UC-07

## Use Case Name

Generate Performance Reports

## Description

This use case allows management to monitor sales and lead management performance.

## Primary Actor

Sales Manager

## Secondary Actor

Regional Operations Manager

## Preconditions

* Data exists in Salesforce.

## Trigger

Manager requests performance report.

## Main Flow

1. User opens reporting dashboard.
2. User selects reporting period.
3. System retrieves data.
4. Dashboard displays KPIs.
5. User reviews metrics.
6. Report exported if required.

## Alternate Flow

3A. No data available.

* System displays informational message.

## Postconditions

* Performance report generated.

## Business Rules

* Reports update in real time.
* Access restricted by user role.

